INT. KITCHEN - NIGHT #1#

= Jane catches Max raiding the fridge.

The fridge door yawns open. Max, mid-bite.

JANE
Again?

EXT. BACKYARD - NIGHT #2#

= Max hides on the porch.

Max sits on the steps, the yogurt half-finished.

INT. INT. JANE'S BEDROOM - NIGHT #3#

= Jane can't sleep.

Jane lies on her back, staring at the ceiling fan.

INT. KITCHEN - MORNING #4#

= Truce over coffee.

Two mugs. Two people pretending nothing happened.

.CAR - DAY #5#

= The drive to work, in silence.

